          "language": "py",
          "contents": "def activate_camera():\n  # Prints a message that the camera is on\n  print(\"Camera is now on.\")\n\ndef open_streaming_tool():\n  # Prints a message that the streaming tool is ready\n  print(\"Streaming tool is ready.\")\n\n# TODO: Write the prepare_stream() function\n\n\n\n# TODO: Call the prepare_stream() function\n\n",
